[l] Die World Anti-Doping Agency wurde von den Russen gehackt (behaupten sie zumindest).The group accessed athlete data, including confidential medical data — such as Therapeutic Use Exemptions delivered by International Sports Federations (IFs) and National Anti-Doping Organizations (NADOs) — related to the Rio Games; and, subsequently released some of the data in the public domain, accompanied by the threat that they will release more.Ein Glueck, dass die Dopingagentur nicht von so Digitalisierungshemmnissen wie Datensparsamkeit behindert wurde!1!!
